        </p>

        <div class="coupon"><%= couponCode %></div>

        <p class="expiry">ðŸŽ¯ Valid until: <%= couponExpiry %></p>

        <p>
          Use this coupon on your next visit. Because birthdays deserve to be
          celebrated in style!
        </p>

        <div class="company-message"><%= companyMessage %></div>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <strong><%= companyTagline %></strong><br />
        &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <%= companyName %>. All rights
        reserved.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
